Package asap.ipaacaadapters

Provides an ipaaca interface to send BML blocks and receive BML feedback.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BMLRealizerToIpaacaAdapter
    Submits BML through ipaaca messages; submits received feedback to registered listeners.
    IpaacaBMLConstants
    Constants for categories and payload keys
    IpaacaBMLSpy
    Listens in on both Ipaaca feedback and bml messages
    IpaacaToBMLRealizerAdapter
    Submits ipaaca messages (from an InputBuffer) to a RealizerPort; submits RealizerPort feedbacks to the OutputBuffer.
